POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (22): PAKISTAN (WILD POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1), NIGERIA (CIRCULATING VACCINE-DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2), VACCINATION CAMPAIGN POSTPONEMENT
